'''''Mission Escape!''''' is an Apple II video game programmed by Jim Jacobson.<ref name=giantlist/> and published by CE Software in 1980. ''Mission Escape!'' is a science fiction game in which the player fights through a series of progressively deadlier rooms, while being attacked by troopers, drones, and robots armed with missiles.<ref name="SG"/>

